-- Anadarko Cut to Junk by Moody's Amid `Uncertainty' Over Gulf Cleanup Cost
-- Vivek Shankar
-- 2010-06-18T21:47:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-18/anadarko-cut-to-junk-by-moody-s-amid-uncertainty-over-gulf-cleanup-cost.html

          
          
             Anadarko Petroleum Corp.’s long-term
debt rating was cut to Ba1, or below investment grade, from Baa3
by Moody’s Investors Service. The rating may be downgraded
further, Moody’s said.  
          
          


  


        